query:
SELECT id, playerName, sourceType, upgradeDetails, timestamp 
FROM upgrade_log 
WHERE sourceType LIKE '%7%' OR sourceType LIKE '%seven%' OR upgradeDetails LIKE '%7GM%'
LIMIT 20
